Package: libgnucash
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Shaun Savage <savages@crmep.com>
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: @DEPENDS@
Homepage: https://www.gnucash.org/
Description: Engine-only libgnucash bundle under /opt/libgnucash/
 Pre-built libgnucash engine (no GUI, no OFX, no AqBanking, no Python)
 packaged for installation under /opt/libgnucash. Built from upstream
 GnuCash source in an isolated container by the rgnucash repo's
 docker/libgnucash/build.sh.
 .
 Exists because GnuCash upstream does not promise a stable C API and
 no Debian/Ubuntu release ships libgnucash-dev. The rgnucash FFI
 crate links against this at build time; downstream daemons (e.g.
 crfactura) link against it at run time.
 .
 Coexists with the system gnucash desktop package — this one lives in
 /opt/libgnucash/lib/, the desktop's engine in /usr/lib/<triplet>/.
